    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person! I've babied this car since day one, and it's still in absolute mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and hasn't seen a single raindrop if I could help it! No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive! \u2728\ud83d\ude97",
      "price": 43900.0,
