    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a meticulously maintained VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically pristine, the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term reliability. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and telepathic steering feedback this chassis is known for. Showroom-grade aesthetics inside and out.",
